-- ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- STEP 1: CLEAN SLATE
-- One statement empties every data table. CASCADE handles the table
-- relationships; RESTART IDENTITY resets the auto-numbering counters.
-- ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
